fields.Subject: [DEV] PrintCounts
fields.Body: -- Base query is done once to speed up subsequent queries.WITH all_labels AS(    SELECT *    FROM print_job_requests    WHERE customer_order_id = 109497348    AND job_type = 1),-- The total number of conveyable license plates we have to print.conveyable_total AS(    SELECT count(*) as count    FROM all_labels    WHERE printer_id IN (2, 17, 47, 48, 49, 51, 52, 56, 57, 77, 148, 2)),-- Total total number of conveyable license plates that have printed.conveyable_printed AS(    SELECT count(*) as count    FROM all_labels    WHERE printer_id IN (2, 17, 47, 48, 49, 51, 52, 56, 57, 77, 148, 2)    AND print_job_id IS NOT NULL),-- The total number of non-conveyable license plates we have to print.-- 2337 ALK #84413 - updated statement to get the correct amount of non-con itemsnoncon_total AS(    SELECT sum(quantity) as count    FROM customer_order_items    WHERE customer_order_id = 109497348    AND license_plate_side=1),-- The total number of non-conveyable license plates that have printed.noncon_printed AS(    SELECT count(*) as count    FROM print_job_requests    WHERE customer_order_id = 109497348    AND job_type = 5    AND printer_id IN (4, 18, 27, 28, 29, 30, 31, 70, 71, 72, 73, 74, 75, 76, 114, 115, 116, 118, 121, 124, 125, 145, 4)    AND print_job_id IS NOT NULL),-- The total number of license plates we have to print for customer pickup.pickup_total AS(    SELECT count(*) as count    FROM all_labels    WHERE printer_id = 62),-- The total number of license plates that have printed for customer pickup.pickup_printed AS(    SELECT count(*) as count    FROM all_labels    WHERE printer_id = 62    AND print_job_id IS NOT NULL)SELECT    (SELECT count FROM conveyable_total) AS conveyable_total,    (SELECT count FROM conveyable_printed) AS conveyable_printed,    (SELECT count FROM noncon_total) AS noncon_total,    (SELECT count FROM noncon_printed) AS noncon_printed,    (SELECT count FROM pickup_total) AS pickup_total,    (SELECT count FROM pickup_printed) AS pickup_printed;Interpreted -
